sourceQuestionId":"369955253577511002","practice":"练习六"},{"id":"ncre3_theory_592","questionStem":"在 MySQL 中，关键字（  ）用于对两个查询结果进行联合操作。","option":["JOIN","MERGE","UNION","LINK"],"answer":"C","type":"singleChoice","sourceQuestionId":"369955253577511003","practice":"练习六"},{"id":"ncre3_theory_593","questionStem":"在 MySQL 中，现数据库中有 A 表，包括学生姓名“name”、学科“course”、成绩“score”等字段，数据表结构如下：\nname        course        score\n张三         语文           80\n张三         数学           90\n李四         语文           70\n李四         数学           80\n李四         英语           90\n能正确统计每个学科的最高分的语句是（  ）。","option":["SELECT course,MAX(score) FROM A GROUP BY name;","SELECT course,MAX(score) FROM A GROUP BY course;","SELECT course,MIN(score) FROM A GROUP BY name;","SELECT course,MIN(score) FROM A GROUP BY course;"],"answer":"B","type":"singleChoice","sourceQuestionId":"369955253577511004","practice":"练习六"},{"id":"ncre3_theory_594","questionStem":"在 MySQL 中，聚合函数（  ）可以用于计算分组中某列的平均值。","option":["SUM(column_name)","COUNT(column_name)","AVG(column_name)","MAX(column_name)"],"answer":"C","type":"singleChoice","sourceQuestionId":"369955253577511005","practice":"练习六"},{"id":"ncre3_theory_595","questionStem":"在 MySQL 中，能在分组后仅返回每组中前两行的语法是（  ）。","option":["LIMIT 2","TOP 2","ROW LIMIT 2","FIRST 2"],"answer":"A","type":"singleChoice","sourceQuestionId":"369955253577511006","practice":"练习六"},{"id":"ncre3_theory_596","questionStem":"在 MySQL 中，能在分组后仅返回满足特定条件组的语法是（  ）。","option":["HAVING condition","FILTER condition","WHERE condition","LIMIT condition"],"answer":"A","type":"singleChoice","sourceQuestionId":"369955253577511007","practice":"练习六"},{"id":"ncre3_theory_597","questionStem":"在 MySQL 中，如果不加任何条件，执行 UPDATE 语句会发生（  ）。","option":["更新表中所有行的数据","更新表中第一行的数据","更新表中最后一行的数据","不会有任何更新操作"],"answer":"A","type":"singleChoice","sourceQuestionId":"369955253577511008","practice":"练习六"},{"id":"ncre3_theory_598","questionStem":"在 MySQL 中，正确使用 UPDATE 语句同时更新多个列的值的语句是（  ）。","option":["UPDATE table_name SET column1 = value1, column2 = value2;","UPDATE table_name MODIFY column1 = value1, MODIFY column2 = value2;","UPDATE table_name ALTER column1 = value1, ALTER column2 = value2;","UPDATE table_name ALL column1 = value1, ALL column2 = value2;"],"answer":"A","type":"singleChoice","sourceQuestionId":"369955253577511009","practice":"练习六"},{"id":"ncre3_theory_599","questionStem":"在 MySQL 中，正确同时更新多个列的值，并设置条件的语句是（  ）。","option":["UPDATE table_name SET column1 = value1, column2 = value2 WHERE condition;","UPDATE table_name MODIFY column1 = value1, MODIFY column2 = value2 WHERE condition;","UPDATE table_name ALTER column1 = value1, ALTER column2 = value2 WHERE condition;","UPDATE table_name SET column1 = value1 AND column2 = value2 WHERE condition;"],"answer":"A","type":"singleChoice","sourceQuestionId":"369955253577511010","practice":"练习六"},{"id":"ncre3_theory_600","questionStem":"在 MySQL 中，如果要将某一列的值增加 10%，正确的 UPDATE 语句是（  ）。","option":["UPDATE table_name SET column1 = column1 + 0.1 WHERE condition;","UPDATE table_name SET column1 = column1 * 1.1 WHERE condition;","UPDATE table_name MODIFY column1 = column1 + 0.1 WHERE condition;","UPDATE table_name SET column1 = column1 - 0.1 WHERE condition;"],"answer":"B","type":"singleChoice","sourceQuestionId":"369955253577511011","practice":"练习六"}]